<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n                \n\n<div class=\"kksr-legend\" style=\"font-size: 19.2px;\">\n            <span class=\"kksr-muted\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 post<\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #d83131;\">GIA S\u01af B\u00ccNH MINH THU\u1ed8C HTCON VI\u1ec6T NAM<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #d83131;\">GIA S\u01af L\u1ecaCH S\u1eec GI\u1eceI &#8211; CHUY\u00caN KH\u1ed0I C &#8211; \u00d4N THI L\u1edaP 9 &#8211; THI \u0110\u1ea0I H\u1eccC<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">D\u1ea0Y TH\u1eec 02 BU\u1ed4I \u0110\u1ea6U TI\u00caN<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd 100% H\u1eccC PH\u00cd N\u1ebeU H\u1eccC SINH KH\u00d4NG HI\u1ec2U B\u00c0I<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">\u00a0<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/demogiasu.vntsc.vn\/uploads\/news\/Gia-Su-Cac-Mon\/Sinh-Hoc\/hot_2.gif\" alt=\"\" \/> Hotline: 0963.138.511 &#8211; 0862.856.500<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\"><strong>GIA S\u01af B\u00ccNH MINH &#8211; CUNG C\u1ea4P GIA S\u01af T\u1ea4T C\u1ea2 C\u00c1C M\u00d4N<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\">\n<table id=\"tablepress-35\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-35\">\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"row-1\">\n\t<th class=\"column-1\">D\u1ea1y k\u00e8m c\u00e1c m\u00f4n v\u0103n h\u00f3a: To\u00e1n, L\u00fd, H\u00f3a, Anh, Ti\u1ec3u H\u1ecdc, Ng\u1eef V\u0103n, L\u1ecbch S\u1eed.... t\u1eeb L\u1edbp 1 \u0111\u1ebfn L\u1edbp 12, \u00d4n thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc.<\/th><th class=\"column-2\">D\u1ea1y k\u00e8m c\u00e1c m\u00f4n ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef: Ti\u1ebfng H\u00e0n, Ti\u1ebfng Trung, Ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt....<\/th><th class=\"column-3\">Luy\u1ec7n thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc, chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ea5p, \u00f4n thi h\u1ecdc sinh gi\u1ecfi... gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc sinh thi \u0111\u1ed7 v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 cao<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody class=\"row-striping row-hover\">\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<!-- #tablepress-35 from cache --><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">Gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0 L\u1ecbch S\u1eed gi\u1ecfi, c\u00f3 nghi\u00eap v\u1ee5 s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p d\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc t\u01b0 duy d\u1ec5 nh\u1edb, d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u&#8230;.. C\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c c\u01a1n b\u1ea3n t\u1edbi luy\u1ec7n thi h\u1ecdc sinh gi\u1ecfi, h\u1ecdc n\u00e2ng cao, chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ea5p l\u1edbp 9, \u00f4n thi \u0110\u1ea1i H\u1ecdc&#8230;.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"I_%E2%80%93_HINH_THUC_GIA_SU_DAY_KEM_MON_LICH_SU\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #ed1c24;\"><strong>I<\/strong>\u00a0&#8211;\u00a0<b>H\u00ccNH TH\u1ee8C GIA S\u01af D\u1ea0Y K\u00c8M M\u00d4N L\u1ecaCH S\u1eec<\/b><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">D\u1ea1y k\u00e8m\u00a0<b>1 gia s\u01b0<\/b>\u00a0\u2013\u00a0<b>1 h\u1ecdc sinh<\/b>\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t (C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc k\u00e8m nh\u00f3m t\u1eeb 2-5 em h\u1ecdc sinh)<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">H\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 h\u1ecdc sinh (Ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc nh\u00e0 gia s\u01b0 do gia \u0111\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh)<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">Ph\u1ee5 huynh, h\u1ecdc sinh \u0111\u01b0a ra y\u00eau c\u1ea7u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0: Sinh vi\u00ean hay gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean, H\u1ecdc kh\u1ed1i ng\u00e0nh, tr\u01b0\u1eddng, qu\u00ea qu\u00e1n, gi\u1edbi t\u00ednh\u2026<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">Th\u1eddi gian h\u1ecdc tu\u1ef3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 gia s\u01b0 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp theo l\u1ecbch r\u1ea3nh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">Th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ecdc: 2h ( C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Ph\u1ee5 huynh, h\u1ecdc sinh)<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"II_%E2%80%93_DOI_NGU_GIA_SU_GIOI_GIAU_KINH_NGHIEM_ON_THI\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #e14d43; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>II &#8211; \u0110\u1ed8I NG\u0168 GIA S\u01af GI\u1eceI, GI\u00c0U KINH NGHI\u1ec6M \u00d4N THI<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #d83131; font-size: 100%;\">GI\u00c1O VI\u00caN<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">+ L\u00e0 c\u00e1c th\u1ea7y c\u00f4 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng, t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh quy khoa s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m L\u1ecbch S\u1eed t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">+ Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ee9ng l\u1edbp t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c trung t\u00e2m l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #d83131; font-size: 100%;\">SINH VI\u00caN<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">+ Gia s\u01b0 chuy\u00ean kh\u1ed1i C, c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m thi \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc m\u00f4n L\u1ecbch s\u1eed cao, ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng: \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, \u0110H s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4, \u0110H gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c &#8211; \u0110H Qu\u1ed1c gia, H\u1ecdc vi\u00ean b\u00e1o ch\u00ed &amp; tuy\u00ean truy\u1ec1n, \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Nh\u00e2n V\u0103n&#8230;.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">+\u00a0\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 sinh vi\u00ean, gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean gi\u1ecfi c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">+ C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t, phong th\u00e1i nghi\u00eam t\u00fac, nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, t\u1ec9 m\u1ec9 v\u00e0 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc sinh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">+ Ki\u1ec3m tra, \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00ec v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean v\u1edbi ph\u1ee5 huynh<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1513\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1513\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-1513\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Gia-su-la-ai-300x212.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"424\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Gia-su-la-ai-300x212.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Gia-su-la-ai.png 748w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1513\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><em>\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gia s\u01b0 c\u1ee7a trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh<\/em><\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"III_%E2%80%93_BANG_GIA_HOC_PHI_GIA_SU_LICH_SU_TAI_NHA\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #ed1c24;\"><strong>III &#8211; B\u1ea2NG GI\u00c1, H\u1eccC PH\u00cd GIA S\u01af L\u1ecaCH S\u1eec T\u1ea0I NH\u00c0<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><h2 id=\"tablepress-31-name\" class=\"tablepress-table-name tablepress-table-name-id-31\">H\u1eccC PH\u00cd - GIA S\u01af L\u1ecaCH S\u1eec T\u1ea0I NH\u00c0<\/h2>\n\n<table id=\"tablepress-31\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-31 tbody-has-connected-cells\" aria-labelledby=\"tablepress-31-name\">\n<tbody class=\"row-striping row-hover\">\n<tr class=\"row-1\">\n\t<td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"column-1\">L\u1edaP H\u1eccC<\/td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"column-2\">SINH VI\u00caN<\/td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"column-4\">GI\u00c1O VI\u00caN<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-2\">\n\t<td class=\"column-2\">1 H\u1ecdc sinh<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">2 H\u1ecdc sinh<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">1 H\u1ecdc sinh<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">2 H\u1ecdc sinh<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-3\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">C\u1ea5p 2<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">120.000 \u2013 150.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">180.000 \u2013 200.000<\/td><td class=\"column-4\"> 250.000 - 300.000<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">300.000 \u2013 350.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-4\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">L\u1edbp 9<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">150.000 - 180.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">180.000 - 250.000<\/td><td class=\"column-4\"> 250.000 - 300.000<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">300.000 - 350.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-5\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">C\u1ea5p 3<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">150.000 - 180.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">200.000 - 250.000<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">250.000 - 300.000<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">350.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-6\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">\u00d4n thi \u0110\u1ea1i H\u1ecdc<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">180.000 - 200.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">250.000 - 300.000<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">250.000 - 350.000<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">350.000 - 400.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-7\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">\u00d4n thi h\u1ecdc sinh gi\u1ecfi, HS chuy\u00ean<\/td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"column-2\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n<\/td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"column-4\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<!-- #tablepress-31 from cache --><\/span><\/p>\n<blockquote>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">&gt;&gt; B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean ch\u1ec9 mang t\u00ednh t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i, h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tu\u1ef3 theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh. Qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng vui l\u00f2ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 Hotline: <span style=\"\">096.31.38.511<\/span> \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #0000ff;\">&gt;&gt; Tham kh\u1ea3o th\u00eam: <\/span><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0<\/span>H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed m\u00f4n <a href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top-3000-gia-su-tieng-anh-tai-nha-tang-hieu-qua-gap-5-lan\/\"><b>gia s\u01b0 ti\u1ebfng anh <\/b><\/a>update m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 <a href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/hoc-phi-bang-gia-gia-su-tai-nha-hn-mon-toan-anh-van-hoa-ly\/\"><strong><span style=\"color: #333399;\">h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed gia s\u01b0<\/span><\/strong><\/a> t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb l\u1edbp 1-12, \u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc, n\u0103ng khi\u1ebfu, ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef&#8230;.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><em><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0<\/em><a href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/bang-gia-500-gia-su-mon-toan-gioi-tu-lop-1-12-o-ha-noi\/\"><span style=\"color: #333399;\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n<\/strong><\/span><\/a> t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u2013 H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb 120k &#8211; gi\u00e1 \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i h\u01a1n h\u1ecdc trung t\u00e2m 20 ng\u01b0\u1eddi &#8211; Hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 g\u1ea5p 5 l\u1ea7n<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"IV_%E2%80%93_CAM_KET_GIA_SU_LICH_SU\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #ed1c24;\"><strong>IV &#8211; CAM K\u1ebeT GIA S\u01af L\u1ecaCH S\u1eec<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h4 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E2%9C%85_Co_hay_khong_duoc_hoc_thu_voi_gia_su_mon_Lich_Su_Ha_Noi\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>\u2705 C\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc th\u1eed v\u1edbi gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n L\u1ecbch S\u1eed H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i?<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\">V\u1edbi ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh, gia s\u01b0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 2 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc th\u1eed. N\u1ebfu trong 2 bu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y, gia s\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi con v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd thu\u00ea gia s\u01b0, th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed n\u00e0o. N\u1ebfu gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y t\u1ed1t, v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh nh\u1eadn gia s\u01b0 th\u00ec 2 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc th\u1eed s\u1ebd t\u00ednh ph\u00ed v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng cho gia s\u01b0.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E2%9C%85_Neu_khong_dong_y_gia_su_nay_thi_phai_lam_sao\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>\u2705\u00a0N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia s\u01b0 n\u00e0y th\u00ec ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m sao?<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\">T\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o, ph\u1ee5 huynh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ed5i gia s\u01b0 sao cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ph\u1ee5 huynh. T\u1ea1i gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh, ph\u00ed t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n, t\u00ecm v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5i gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd<\/span><\/p>\n<h4 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E2%9C%85_Phu_huynh_co_duoc_kiem_tra_ly_lich_gia_su_khong\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\"><strong>\u2705\u00a0Ph\u1ee5 huynh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m tra l\u00fd l\u1ecbch gia s\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng?<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\">M\u1ecdi th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a <strong>gia s\u01b0 L\u1ecbch S\u1eed<\/strong>\u00a0bao g\u1ed3m s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00ed l\u1ecbch v\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng khai v\u1edbi ph\u1ee5 huynh. Khi qua gia \u0111\u00ecnh d\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc, sinh vi\u00ean v\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t tr\u00ecnh th\u1ebb cho ph\u1ee5 huynh.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3494\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3494\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3494\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/gia-su-mon-lich-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/gia-su-mon-lich-su.png 1200w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/gia-su-mon-lich-su-300x250.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/gia-su-mon-lich-su-1024x853.png 1024w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/gia-su-mon-lich-su-768x640.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3494\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><em>Gia s\u01b0 gi\u1ecfi d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m m\u00f4n L\u1ecbch S\u1eed t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/em><\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\">&gt;&gt;&gt; G\u1ecdi ngay Hotline: <span style=\"\">096.31.38.511<\/span> ho\u1eb7c <span style=\"\">0862.856.500<\/span> ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n 24\/7 m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a con b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff; font-size: 100%;\">Xem th\u00eam c\u00e1c m\u00f4n kh\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\">&gt;&gt;&gt;<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"> <a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top1-gia-su-van-ha-noi-bang-gia-mon-van-moi-nhat-2018\/\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 V\u0103n<\/strong><\/a><\/span> t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 cho con &#8211; C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 sau 01 th\u00e1ng<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\">&gt